        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Supplemental table S1 contains 698 synaptic proteins identified in three different experimental approaches: isolated PSD preparation, MAGUK-associated signalling complexes (MASC) and AMPA receptor complexes (ARCs).\nAK1A1 was found as akr1a1.. Experimental description: Here we present a large-scale proteomic analysis of the\npostsynaptic proteome (PSP) of mouse brain. p.17" ;
